{"componentChunkName":"component---antv-gatsby-theme-antv-site-templates-tutorial-tsx","path":"/en/tutorials/table-virtual","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Choerodon UI","githubUrl":"https://github.com/open-hand/choerodon-ui","tutorials":[]},"pathPrefix":"/choerodon-ui"},"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>In this chapter, we introduce how to enable virtual scrolling in Table for large data scenarios.</p>\n<h1 id=\"use-cases\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#use-cases\" aria-label=\"use cases permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Use Cases</h1>\n<p>Virtual scrolling can be enabled if any of the following situations apply:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Interaction or scrolling lags due to the complexity of the Table.</li>\n<li>Horizontal scrolling results in blank areas when the Table has many columns.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>There are two ways to use virtual scrolling:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Enable virtual scrolling globally</li>\n<li>Set virtual scrolling for a single Table component</li>\n</ol>\n<h1 id=\"supported-versions\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#supported-versions\" aria-label=\"supported versions permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Supported Versions</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>Older version</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Choerodon-ui >= 1.4.2</p>\n<p>To enable virtual scrolling globally: configure the <code class=\"language-text\">tableVirtual</code> and <code class=\"language-text\">tableVirtualCell</code> properties.</p>\n<p>For a Table component: configure the <code class=\"language-text\">virtual</code> and <code class=\"language-text\">virtualCell</code> properties.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>New version</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Choerodon-ui >= 1.6.2</p>\n<p>To enable virtual scrolling globally: configure the <code class=\"language-text\">tableVirtual</code> property or use the callback function style within the <code class=\"language-text\">tableVirtual</code> property. Optionally, the <code class=\"language-text\">tableVirtualBuffer</code> property can also be set.</p>\n<p>For a Table component: configure the <code class=\"language-text\">virtual</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">columnBuffer</code>, and <code class=\"language-text\">columnThreshold</code> properties.</p>\n<p><strong>The new version is backward compatible with the old version's syntax by default.</strong></p>\n<h1 id=\"instructions\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#instructions\" aria-label=\"instructions permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Instructions</h1>\n<p>The new version adds <code class=\"language-text\">columnBuffer</code> and <code class=\"language-text\">columnThreshold</code> properties to the Table component compared with the old version. For the global <code class=\"language-text\">tableVirtual</code> configuration, a callback function style has been added.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>columnBuffer\nExplanation: Defines the column buffer when virtual scrolling is enabled. That is, besides the columns visible on the page, <code class=\"language-text\">columnBuffer</code> columns are pre-rendered. After scrolling, <code class=\"language-text\">columnBuffer</code> columns on both sides of the visible area are also pre-rendered. (In the old version, enabling <code class=\"language-text\">virtualCell</code> only pre-renders 1 column.)</li>\n<li>columnThreshold\nExplanation: Defines the threshold for dynamically loading columns when virtual scrolling is enabled. That is, during horizontal scrolling, columns are loaded in batches of <code class=\"language-text\">columnThreshold</code>. (In the old version, columns are loaded one by one during horizontal scrolling, increasing the rendering frequency.)</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"usage\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#usage\" aria-label=\"usage permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Usage</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>Old Version Usage (Choerodon-ui >= 1.4.2)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Global enabling configuration:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> configure <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'choerodon-ui'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token function\">configure</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  tableVirtual<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  tableVirtualCell<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Table-specific enabling configuration:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>Table\n  <span class=\"token comment\">//...</span>\n  virtual\n  virtualCell\n  style<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> height<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">300</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Set virtual and table height to enable virtual scrolling</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>New Version Usage</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Global enabling configuration:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> configure <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'choerodon-ui'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token function\">configure</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token function-variable function\">tableVirtual</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">rows<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> columns</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> rows <span class=\"token operator\">*</span> columns <span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token number\">3000</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  tableVirtualBuffer<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> columnBuffer<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> columnThreshold<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">5</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>The above tableVirtual uses a callback to determine whether to enable virtual scrolling, meaning virtual scrolling is enabled only when the Table cells exceed 3000, otherwise it remains off.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Table-specific enabling configuration:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>Table\n  <span class=\"token comment\">//...</span>\n  virtual\n  columnBuffer<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token number\">5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  columnThreshold<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token number\">5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  style<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> height<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">300</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Set virtual and table height to enable virtual scrolling</span></code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>In the new version, it is not recommended to enable the virtualCell property when using virtual scrolling, since the columnBuffer property can replace it.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h1 id=\"notes\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#notes\" aria-label=\"notes permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Notes</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>A Table height must be specified to enable virtual scrolling.</strong></li>\n<li>In the new version, the default values for columnBuffer and columnThreshold are both 3, which works for most Table scenarios. Usually, no configuration is needed, but these values can be adjusted based on the complexity of the table.</li>\n<li><strong>The value of columnBuffer needs to be greater than or equal to the value of columnThreshold</strong>. Otherwise, noticeable blank spaces may appear during horizontal scrolling.</li>\n<li>The performance of virtual scrolling is affected by the width, height, and row height of the Table. The smaller the width and height of the Table, the better the performance; the larger the row height, the better the performance as well.</li>\n</ul>","htmlAst":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"In this chapter, we introduce how to enable virtual scrolling in Table for large data scenarios."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h1","properties":{"id":"use-cases","style":"position:relative;"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#use-cases","ariaLabel":"use cases permalink","className":["anchor","before"]},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"svg","properties":{"ariaHidden":"true","focusable":"false","height":"16","version":"1.1","viewBox":"0 0 16 16","width":"16"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"path","properties":{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"},"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"Use Cases"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Virtual scrolling can be enabled if any of the following situations apply:"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"ul","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Interaction or scrolling lags due to the complexity of the Table."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Horizontal scrolling results in blank areas when the Table has many columns."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"There are two ways to use virtual scrolling:"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"ol","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Enable virtual scrolling globally"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Set virtual scrolling for a single Table component"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h1","properties":{"id":"supported-versions","style":"position:relative;"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#supported-versions","ariaLabel":"supported versions permalink","className":["anchor","before"]},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"svg","properties":{"ariaHidden":"true","focusable":"false","height":"16","version":"1.1","viewBox":"0 0 16 16","width":"16"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"path","properties":{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"},"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"Supported Versions"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"ul","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Older version"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Choerodon-ui >= 1.4.2"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"To enable virtual scrolling globally: configure the "},{"type":"element","tagName":"code","properties":{"className":["language-text"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"tableVirtual"}]},{"type":"text","value":" and "},{"type":"element","tagName":"code","properties":{"className":["language-text"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"tableVirtualCell"}]},{"type":"text","value":" properties."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"For a Table component: configure the "},{"type":"element","tagName":"code","properties":{"className":["language-text"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"virtual"}]},{"type":"text","value":" and "},{"type":"element","tagName":"code","properties":{"className":["language-text"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"virtualCell"}]},{"type":"text","value":" properties."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"ul","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"New version"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Choerodon-ui >= 1.6.2"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"To enable virtual scrolling globally: configure the "},{"type":"element","tagName":"code","properties":{"className":["language-text"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"tableVirtual"}]},{"type":"text","value":" property or use the callback function style within the "},{"type":"element","tagName":"code","properties":{"className":["language-text"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"tableVirtual"}]},{"type":"text","value":" property. Optionally, the "},{"type":"element","tagName":"code","properties":{"className":["language-text"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"tableVirtualBuffer"}]},{"type":"text","value":" property can also be set."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"For a Table component: configure the "},{"type":"element","tagName":"code","properties":{"className":["language-text"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"virtual"}]},{"type":"text","value":", "},{"type":"element","tagName":"code","properties":{"className":["language-text"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"columnBuffer"}]},{"type":"text","value":", and "},{"type":"element","tagName":"code","properties":{"className":["language-text"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"columnThreshold"}]},{"type":"text","value":" properties."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"strong","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"The new version is backward compatible with the old version's syntax by default."}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h1","properties":{"id":"instructions","style":"position:relative;"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#instructions","ariaLabel":"instructions permalink","className":["anchor","before"]},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"svg","properties":{"ariaHidden":"true","focusable":"false","height":"16","version":"1.1","viewBox":"0 0 16 16","width":"16"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"path","properties":{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"},"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"Instructions"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"The new version adds "},{"type":"element","tagName":"code","properties":{"className":["language-text"